# Local Context Compiler requires NO API keys and makes NO network calls.
#
# This file exists only to document that fact and to reserve a place for
# optional, local-only settings in the future. Copy it to `.env` if you like,
# but the MVP reads nothing from the environment.
#
# Do NOT put secrets, API keys, or private documents in this repository.
#
# (reserved for future optional settings)
# LCC_DEFAULT_MODEL=gpt-4.1
